\f2\fs48 \cf2 \cb3 Sessions with shopping cart checkout\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa480\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs32 \cf2 You can run the following query to view how many sessions end up with checkout (POST call to the /cart/checkout service):\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 SELECT\
 JSON_VALUE(json_payload.session),\
 COUNT(*)\
FROM\
 `qwiklabs-gcp-00-a1958137b546.global.day2ops-log._AllLogs`\
WHERE\
 JSON_VALUE(json_payload['http.req.method']) = "POST"\
 AND JSON_VALUE(json_payload['http.req.path']) = "/cart/checkout"\
 AND timestamp > TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 1 HOUR)\
GROUP BY\
 JSON_VALUE(json_payload.session)\cb1 \
\
